Comment: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*sign: To Ryu
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:10.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:16.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:20.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's first sleepover...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:23.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your dad supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:34.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say hi to her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:39.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to give them those youkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:41.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's my first sleepover.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:02:00.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying at Chizu-chan's place, together with Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:11.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:16.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:27.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, your sleepover kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:39.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't come to my house tomorrow or the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:40.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you piss him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:55.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:03:00.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so going to play games to cheer Yano-chin up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go ahead and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's Ryu's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to go to Ryu's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:14.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember how you might have pissed him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:19.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kicked him out last time he came over, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:24.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He almost saw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?! He's such a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now {\i1}you're{\i0} pissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come to my house tomorrow or the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:46.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? It's Ryu's birthday the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu, let's go gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't say not to come today, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go make up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him your birthday present too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he get upset over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All-in huh? Who would have thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross-counter for the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the boss right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the boss tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:39.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you haven't told her yet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:43.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:48.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can just meet my brother during New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:54.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I especially wanted him to meet Chizuru anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's there so many of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:00.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to cheer Joe up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, my break-up buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:16.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, let's do a double cheer-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:30.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people get dumped and comfort each other, then fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be here tonight, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys shuffle over then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:59.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone have any good news to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there wouldn't be any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, why did you split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.60,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:19.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping at a friend's place, being with so many people, talking about love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... oh yeah, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumping into the person I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:32.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,All this stuff is really happening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu, could you get me a cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:40.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ramen's so awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.80,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And give him this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, what's your type of guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:00.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A laid back, easy going, mature guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:25.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit hurt when you kicked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't really about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:37.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to hide something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wasn't there something you wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you coming home tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got off work early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's gotten long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the person Chizu-chan likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're Chizuru's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.79,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,High school friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako and Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put her in the closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in pajamas and jeans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have worn my old miniskirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ryu, why haven't you told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any more luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu, get a grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.43,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid's my brother, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katayama Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:57.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Chizuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call her Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:06.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved her like a little sister since she was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katayama. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:24.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the neighborhood, my name's Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:32.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really family or a relative or anything, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cold, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Married?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's back home, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sort of came here at an important time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, outsiders, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:18.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already? I'm not boss anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an outsider too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're all going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm strong anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:58.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she's thinking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I'd said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:20.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be uncomfortable if she thought I told her because I was being nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:28.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind her getting angry, but I think she'd be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:35.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been worried about Yoshida the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:40.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not upset or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:55.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I really worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:04.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he must like Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:16.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I win again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been playing for four hours straight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:38.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:44.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I haven't even said congratulations to him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go see him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:55.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved brother-like friend's getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more fish in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:13.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I ended up getting us all kicked out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:19.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a crush for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even going to look at me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to become an awesome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows once I'm grown up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryu's brother that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:42.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing a miniskirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:46.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she didn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she didn't sleep to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice sweater, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hand-me-down from my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:57.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hole here, but whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:31.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she'd bitch and moan like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:39.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell if she was sad or not at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:48.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:53.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even hear her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's anything we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:07.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so happy to wear a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:17.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't cheer her up or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:23.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no words for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:41.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all times, this time I had nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:51.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What are friends supposed to do when this happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's having a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a daughter? Except not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:13.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a younger sister? Except not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a relative or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:22.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What's some kid from the block doing here on such an important occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid from the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Let's fight, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}I'll kill you if you don't hit me with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make girls cry, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:56.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye boo boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, look, I have a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:15.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I express my love with bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:26.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru'd always laugh about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:35.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru often had a girlfriend with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:39.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but it never really lasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:42.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought he was just dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:49.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So my dream was always to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:13.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not the one to realize that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:35.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings unconveyed, tears overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode: Present
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
